00:00:35.000 --> 00:00:41.000
So that's the name.

00:00:41.000 --> 00:00:48.000
I'm from Nigeria, the eastern part of Nigeria.

00:00:48.000 --> 00:00:57.000
And from the region of the, I call Anambra state,

00:00:57.000 --> 00:01:06.000
and from the area of the Igbo-speaking dialects.

