I was born on the 22nd of November 1944.

00:01:22.000 --> 00:01:30.000
I was born as twins, identical twins.

00:01:30.000 --> 00:01:36.000
And both of us as Haido, we grew up and...

00:01:37.000 --> 00:01:42.000
Are you able to say just your name and where you were born in the dialect?

00:01:42.000 --> 00:01:44.000
In one of your dialects?

00:01:44.000 --> 00:01:45.000
In my dialect?

00:01:45.000 --> 00:01:46.000
Yeah.

00:01:46.000 --> 00:01:47.000
Where I was born?

00:01:47.000 --> 00:01:50.000
Yes, and your name and where you were born.

00:01:50.000 --> 00:01:57.000
My name is Cordelia Ukusogwu.

